<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Kale Nilitembea TZR22</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Kale nilitembea
 Nikilemewa dhambi
 Nilikosa msaada,
 kuniponya mateso.

[V2]
 Usifiwe Msalaba!
 Lisifiwe kaburi!
 Linalozidi yote,
 Asifiwe Mwokozi!

[V3]
 Hata nilipofika,
 Mahali pa Msalaba,
 Palinifaa sana,
 Sitasahau kamwe.

[V4]
 Hicho ndicho chanzo,
 Cha kufurahi kwangu.
 Hapo ndipo mzigo,
 Uliponituliwa.

[V5]
 Panapo msalaba,
 Kinatolewa cheti,
 Cha kuingia Mbinguni,
 Kisicho cha kanisa.

[V6]
 Yule Bwana mjinga,
 Likwenda bila cheti,
 Kitumai kwingia,
 Kama walio nacho.

[V7]
 Lipofika langoni,
 Akaulizwa cheti,
 Cha kumwonyesha Bwana,
 Akakutwa hanacho.

[V8]
 Lituhuzunishalo,
 Ni ninyi msio nacho,
 Kuwa kama mjinga,
 Kwa siku ya arusi!

[V9]
 Ubavuni mwa Yesu,
 Mlitokea damu,
 Chemchemi ya uzima,
 Itakasayo roho.

[V10]
 Jitahidi wingie,
 Damuni mwa Mwokozi,
 Utafutiwa dhambi,
 Toka rohoni mwako</lyrics>
<hymn_number>22</hymn_number>
</song>